The hum cause Halucigen to look away, loosing contact with FZ's 
mind, but also making him drive his tail the ince down towards FZ's 
foot where if it drove in successfully would allow Halucigen control 
of FZ for a small amount of time.  Halucigen unfortuantly found 
nothing of much importance, besides the message to the dark lord, 
and a message to a new being.  He would get to this being, and 
bring him as his own. Then meet the Dark One.  But why would FZ 
have a contact with him as well. It was all very confusing.
